title: What will bring the most value to EGGS?
body:
Vote for which option you think will bring the most value to the EGGS token. This is weighted voting. You may vote for more than 1. We may implement more than 1. 

Explanation of Choices:

1. Make NFTs for new upcoming collections available for purchase using EGGS.

2. Divert a percentage of upcoming Chic-A-Dees sales into buying back EGGS directly on Uniswap or Sushiswap so they can be traded for ETH.

3.  Divert a percentage of upcoming Chic-A-Dees royalties into buying back EGGS directly on Uniswap or Sushiswap so they can be traded for ETH.

4. Create a Chic-A-Dees game where the EGGS are used for a valuable purpose or currency within the game. We may also partner to have the EGGS integrated into an existing game.
